  "body_html": "The thymus is an organ of the immune system located in the anterior superior mediastinum. It is located anterior to the heart and posterior to the sternum.<br /><br />It is made up of 2 lobes and has a cortex and a medulla.  It is the site of maturation of T-lymphocytes.  It regresses after puberty.<br /><br /><i>Diagram illustrating position of Thymus in an adult</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb082b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb082.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymus'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb082b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb297b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb297.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymus'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb297b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">1</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">2</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Anatomy</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Head & neck anatomy</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nThe thymus is an organ of the immune system located in the anterior superior mediastinum. It is located anterior to the heart and posterior to the sternum.<br /><br />It is made up of 2 lobes and has a cortex and a medulla.  It is the site of maturation of T-lymphocytes.  It regresses after puberty.<br /><br /><i>Diagram illustrating position of Thymus in an adult</i><br /><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb082b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb082.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymus'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb082b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER><br /><CENTER><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb297b.jpg'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb297.jpg'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymus'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_FRCEMtutor/swb297b.jpg'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></CENTER></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br>",
